S.FORM: Tomislav Nikoli I 1952 a miheca saka 2 folad saka 15 a romi'ad masofoc ci Tomislav Nikoli , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Serbia anini i ci Tomislav Nikoli , patirengan a romi'ad i 2012 a miheca saka 5 folad saka 31 a romi'ad.
